ORIGINAL DESIGN CONTRIBUTIONS
============================================================================

 The following were originated by Patrik Fogoš (FogyXT) as part of the
 JARVIS project, first published in this repository in June 2026:

 - Standby Neuron Agents (tools/memory_agents.py)
 - Neurogenesis / agent self-pruning (tools/memory_agents.py)
 - Five-tier biologically-inspired memory architecture
 - Ebbinghaus-curve episodic scoring (tools/episodic_memory.py)

 These are licensed under AGPL-3.0 as above. See "Commercial licensing"
 in README.md for alternative terms.

